ine-mode-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-launch-issues-looking-into-offline-mode-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-launch-issues-looking-into-offline-mode-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-launch-issues-looking-into-offline-mode-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-launch-issues-looking-into-offline-mode-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/payday-3"><em>《收获日 3</em></a> 》的发行问题非常严重，以至于<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/starbreeze">Starbreeze</a>正在考虑取消其有争议的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-will-have-an-always-online-requirement-3469437">始终在线要求</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/payday-3-review-3501644"><em>《收获日 3》</em>评论：一部有趣的犯罪惊悚片，但不会吸引任何人的心</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>《收获日 3</em> 》于 9 月 21 日在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PS5</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a>上推出，由于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-developer-apologises-for-nightmare-server-issues-at-launch-3503549">服务器连接时断时续、崩溃、持续的匹配问题以及在 PS5 上玩的游戏版本不正确，</a>成为 X 等社交媒体网站上的热门话题。</p><p>考虑到<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/payday-2">《收获日 2》</a>已经过去十年了，</em>这些问题让那些满怀期待地等待第三款游戏的玩家感到烦恼。 Starbreeze 的首席执行官表示，在这些不幸事件发生后，团队将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-developer-apologises-for-nightmare-server-issues-at-launch-3503549">“不懈地努力”</a> ，以确保<em>《收获日 3》</em>能够再次满足他们的期望。</p><p>在<a href="https://news.cision.com/starbreeze-ab/r/payday--3-update,c3841103" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一份官方声明</a>中，开发商解释说，“匹配软件遇到了不可预见的错误”，这导致处理游戏的第三方匹配合作伙伴超载。 </p><figure id="attachment_3499707" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3499707" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3499707" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3499707" class="wp-caption-text"> 《收获日 3》来源：Starbreeze</figcaption></figure><p>它重申，这个问题在<em>《收获日 3》</em>的技术测试版或抢先体验期都没有出现，团队致力于立即解决该问题。</p><p> “从短期来看，这意味着Starbreeze的重点是保证玩家体验。从长远来看，这意味着评估新的配对服务合作伙伴，并减少<em>《收获日 3》</em>对在线服务的依赖。”</p><p>首席执行官 Tobias Sjögren <a href="https://twitter.com/tobiassjogren/status/1705974980972798146" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在发给 X 的帖子中</a>澄清了该声明的后半部分。 “团队正在考虑添加某种离线模式的可能性，”他说。</p><p> <em>《收获日》</em>的创作者之一乌尔夫·安德森 (Ulf Andersson) 曾表示， <em>《收获日 3》</em>可能与其前作有点过于相似。 </p><figure id="attachment_3474739" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3474739" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3474739" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/payday-3-pc-playtests-next-week-2.jpg" alt="发薪日3" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/payday-3-pc-playtests-next-week-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/payday-3-pc-playtests-next-week-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/payday-3-pc-playtests-next-week-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/payday-3-pc-playtests-next-week-2-696x442.jpg 696w, h